# GitLab CE + Container Registry + GitLab Runner (Local Production Setup)

## Overview

This guide installs:

* GitLab CE
* GitLab Container Registry
* GitLab Runner
* Self-Signed Certificate Authority (CA)
* Docker-based deployment
* Local DNS via `/etc/hosts`
* Docker Registry support
* Backup configuration

Environment:

```text
Ubuntu 24.04 LTS
Docker CE
GitLab CE 19.x
GitLab Runner 19.x
Local Network Only
Self-Signed SSL
```

---

# VM Requirements

Minimum:

```text
CPU: 4 vCPU
RAM: 8 GB
Disk: 100 GB SSD
Ubuntu: 24.04 LTS
```

Recommended:

```text
CPU: 8 vCPU
RAM: 16 GB
Disk: 200+ GB SSD
```

