# Common Problems

## SSL Error

Install:

```bash
local-ca.crt
```

into:

```text
Mac Keychain
Windows Trusted Root CA
Linux CA Store
```

---

## Runner Missing config.toml

Verify:

```bash
ls -la runner/config
```

Must contain:

```text
config.toml
```

---

## Registry Login Fails

Verify:

```bash
ls /etc/docker/certs.d/registry.docker.loc
```

Must contain:

```text
ca.crt
```

Restart Docker:

```bash
sudo systemctl restart docker
```


